<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Facture #{{ facture.id }} - MediPlus</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Header */
        .invoice-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #008cba;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .invoice-header .logo {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #008cba;
        }
        .invoice-header img {
            max-height: 50px;
        }

        .invoice-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .invoice-title h1 {
            color: #008cba;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .invoice-title h2 {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .details {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .details .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 120px;
            display: inline-block;
            color: #555;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        table thead {
            background-color: #008cba;
            color: #fff;
        }
        table thead th {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        table tbody tr td {
            padding: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
        .text-right {
            text-align: right;
        }
        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Footer / Signature */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #888;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .signature .sign-line {
            display: inline-block;
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            width: 200px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .signature p {
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="invoice-header">
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="public/assets-front/img/logo.png" alt="MediPlus Logo">
    </div>
    <div>
        <strong>MediPlus - Clinique</strong><br>
        123 Avenue du Centre, 75000 Tunis<br>
        Téléphone: +24 55 26 62
    </div>
</div>

<div class="invoice-title">
    <h1>Facture #{{ facture.id }}</h1>
    <h2>Date: {{ facture.date ? facture.date|date('d/m/Y') : 'N/A' }}</h2>
</div>

<div class="details">
    <span class="label">Nom du Patient:</span> {{ facture.rendez ? facture.rendez.user.nameUser : 'N/A' }}<br>
    <span class="label">ID Patient:</span> {{ facture.rendez ? facture.rendez.user.id : 'N/A' }}<br>
    <span class="label">Montant:</span> {{ facture.montant }} DT
</div>

<table>
    <thead>
    <tr>
        <th>Prestation</th>
        <th class="text-right">Prix (DT)</th>
    </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    <!-- Example items: if your invoice has details, list them. Otherwise, skip -->
    <tr>
        <td>Consultation Médicale</td>
        <td class="text-right">{{ facture.montant }}</td>
    </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<div class="signature">
    <div class="sign-line"></div>
    <p>Médecin / Responsable Clinique</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    Merci pour votre confiance.<br>
    Ceci est un document généré par voie électronique - aucune signature manuscrite n’est nécessaire.
</div>

</body>
</html>
